==评论==
=== 和Adblock Plus的争端 ===
2009年5月1日，Firefox扩展[[Adblock_Plus|Adblock Plus]]的作者Wladimir Palant，宣布一周之前的NoScript 1.9.2版开始妨碍Adblock Plus正常工作。NoScript会在未经Adblock Plus和用户允许的情况下解析并显示赞助商页面。Palant说NoScript使用了[[代码混淆|代码混淆]]来逃避十六进制代码层面对这个修改的检测。<ref name="abp-anu">{{cite web | url = http://adblockplus.org/blog/attention-noscript-users | title = Attention NoScript users | work = Adblock Plus and (a little) more | first = Wladimir | last = Palant | date = 2009-05-01 | publisher = Wladimir Palant | location = [[科隆|科隆]] | accessdate = 2009-05-02 | archive-date = 2012-02-18 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/65XuuyZs9?url=http://adblockplus.org/blog/attention-noscript-users | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = http://noscript.net/downloads/mrd.js.html |title = mrd.js |accessdate = 2010-04-25 |archive-date = 2012-02-18 |archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/65XuwUdql?url=http://noscript.net/downloads/mrd.js.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>几乎同时，[[Mozilla|Mozilla]]因此次事件决定修改社区准则。<ref>{{cite web | title = No Surprises | url = http://blog.mozilla.com/addons/2009/05/01/no-surprises/ | date = 2009-05-01 | accessdate = 2010-04-25 | archive-date = 2010-04-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100420062851/http://blog.mozilla.com/addons/2009/05/01/no-surprises/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>4月30日，NoScript升级到1.9.2.3，把传说中的代码混淆改为了一个用户可见的特性，即NoScript在Adblock Plus的过滤规则中将自己的网站设置为白名单。Wladimir Palant指出这个过滤规则即便被用户删除也会在每次启动的时候自动添加回去，不过这看起来似乎只是个无意的Bug，因为白名单同时也可以被永久禁止或是如NoScript FAQ所说，被用户自己的过滤规则覆盖。<ref name="ns-abp-faq"> Some hours later, on May 2, 2009, a further automatic NoScript update (version 1.9.2.6) completely removed the Adblock Plus whitelist, and public apologies were given on the release notes page for having modified Adblock Plus' behavior without asking users' consent in advance.</ref>几小时之后，2009年5月2日，自动更新的NoScript 1.9.2.6版彻底移除了这一白名单，并在发行记录中对没有在用户事先允许的情况下修改Adblock Plus功能的行为作出公开道歉。<ref>{{cite web | title = NoScript 1.9.2.6 release notes page | url = http://noscript.net/?ver=1.9.2.6 | date = 2009-05-02 | accessdate = 2010-04-25 | archive-date = 2019-10-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191018224355/https://noscript.net/?ver=1.9.2.6 | dead-url = no }}</ref>2009年5月4日，在博客上一篇长文中，NoScript的作者Giorgio Maone以个人身份对最初含糊的说法表达了歉意，认识到这是破坏了信任关系并对此表示后悔。他同时解释NoScript添加的Adblock Plus白名单是对EasyList反常性“攻击”的对抗，这些攻击针对Manoe的网站，并几乎破坏了页面所有的动态功能，甚至是安装NoScript软件包的链接。<ref name="ns-abp-apo">{{cite web | url = http://hackademix.net/2009/05/04/dear-adblock-plus-and-noscript-users-dear-mozilla-community/ | title = Dear Adblock Plus and NoScript Users, Dear Mozilla Community | work = Hackademix.net | date = 2009-05-04 | first = Giorgio | last = Maone | accessdate = 2009-05-18 | archive-date = 2012-02-18 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/65XuvVr3n?url=http://hackademix.net/2009/05/04/dear-adblock-plus-and-noscript-users-dear-mozilla-community/ | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

=== NoScript网站和Ghostery扩展的冲突 ===
2009年5月1日<ref>[http://forums.informaction.com/viewtopic.php?p=3133#p3128 NoScript support forum] {{Wayback|url=http://forums.informaction.com/viewtopic.php?p=3133#p3128 |date=20100125234332 }} "Re: Latest NoScript version (1.9.2) breaks Adblock Plus", comment #3133, Guest (2009-05-01)</ref>以及2009年5月3日<ref>[http://forums.informaction.com/viewtopic.php?p=3610#p3610 NoScript support forum] {{Wayback|url=http://forums.informaction.com/viewtopic.php?p=3610#p3610 |date=20090618163731 }} "Re: Latest NoScript version (1.9.2) breaks Adblock Plus", comment #3610, Curious Inquiry (2009-05-03)</ref>在讨论NoScript对Adblock Plus的修改时，有人在NoScript支持论坛中指出NoScript官网上有一个[[CSS|CSS]]规则不停让[[Ghostery|Ghostery]]这个[[Firefox扩展列表|Mozilla扩展]]弹出提示，表示网页上有奇怪而隐蔽的"bug"。Ghostery也会提示用户Manoe网站上[[Google_Adsense|Google Adsense]]的使用。Manoe在回应中宣称他的CSS没有做出这些，Ghostery的提示是由于其自身的技术问题，同时这些提示看起来很糟糕而且妨碍了网页真实效果的展示。<ref>[http://forums.informaction.com/viewtopic.php?p=3133#p3133 NoScript support forum] {{Wayback|url=http://forums.informaction.com/viewtopic.php?p=3133#p3133 |date=20100125234332 }} "Re: Latest NoScript version (1.9.2) breaks Adblock Plus", comment #3133, Giorgio Maone (2009-05-01)</ref>在之后的声明中Manoe又特别批评这些提示挡住了了捐款按钮和使用许可的显示<ref>[http://forums.informaction.com/viewtopic.php?p=3704#p3704 NoScript support forum] {{Wayback|url=http://forums.informaction.com/viewtopic.php?p=3704#p3704 |date=20090618163735 }} "Re: Latest NoScript version (1.9.2) breaks Adblock Plus", comment #3704, Giorgio Maone (2009-05-04)</ref><ref name="comment3935">[http://forums.informaction.com/viewtopic.php?p=3935#p3935 NoScript support forum] {{Wayback|url=http://forums.informaction.com/viewtopic.php?p=3935#p3935 |date=20090618163755 }} "Re: Additional steps to regain and retain user trust", comment #3935, Giorgio Maone (2009-05-06)</ref>并且表示他的CSS没有阻止Ghostery的正常工作。<ref>[http://ghosterynews.disqus.com/attention_all_noscript_users/#comment-9007251 Ghostery News] {{Wayback|url=http://ghosterynews.disqus.com/attention_all_noscript_users/#comment-9007251 |date=20090618060721 }} "Attention all NoScript users", comment by Giorgio Maone, (2009-05-05)</ref>

大多数人则认为Manoe的CSS文件包含了足够多的统计代码，Ghostery的判断并没有错。有人指出Ghostery在其原始状态的提示并没有挡住Manoe的捐款按钮，并在几秒钟之后就消失了。另外，用户们指出Manoe的一行样式使得Ghostery无法提供一个网页bug的信息，并认为总体上来说这是Manoe自己的问题。但Manoe仍坚称Ghostery显示信息的方式不合适和过度敏感而导致两个扩展出现了矛盾。

这件事的讨论扩展到了第三方站点，<ref>[http://twitter.com/diveintomark/status/1690499472 Twitter] {{Wayback|url=http://twitter.com/diveintomark/status/1690499472 |date=20091116200304 }} tweet by Mark Pilgrim (diveintomark) (2009-05-03)</ref><ref>[http://yardley.ca/2009/05/04/when-blockers-block-the-blockers/ yardley.ca] {{Wayback|url=http://yardley.ca/2009/05/04/when-blockers-block-the-blockers/ |date=20090508023124 }} "When blockers block the blockers", Greg Yardley (2009-05-04)</ref>有些人谎称干扰了Ghostery工作的是NoScript扩展而不是Manoe的站点。Ghostery的作者[http://www.google.com/profiles/dcancel David Cancel]{{Wayback|url=http://www.google.com/profiles/dcancel |date=20100604023024 }}原先发表了一些过激言论但随后修正了。<ref>[http://news.ghostery.com/post/103180001/attention-all-noscript-users Ghostery News] {{Wayback|url=http://news.ghostery.com/post/103180001/attention-all-noscript-users |date=20100425103006 }} "Attention all NoScript users", David Cancel (2009-05-03)</ref>

2009年5月6日，在此事的激烈讨论平息之后，Maone公开表示他改变了自己的观点，为此他修改了自己站点的CSS。<ref name="comment3935"/>Ghostery的提示框不再被隐藏而是向页面中部轻微移动了一些，以免挡住捐款按钮或是许可信息。

